---
// Despedida.astro - Quinceañera Edition ✨
---

<section class="py-12 px-4 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <!-- 🌸 FLORES SUPERIORES -->
      <!-- <div class="flex justify-center mb-8" id="flores-arriba-despedida">
        <img
          src="/imagenes/FlorSeparador.webp"
          alt="Flores decorativas"
          class="w-32 md:w-56 lg:w-64 h-auto object-contain"
        />
      </div> -->

      <!-- CARD GLASSMORPHISM -->
      <div
        class="cal-card rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12 relative"
        id="card-despedida"
      >
        <!-- Destellos -->
        <div class="sparkle sparkle-1"></div>
        <div class="sparkle sparkle-2"></div>
        <div class="sparkle sparkle-3"></div>

        <!-- Esquinas decorativas -->
        <div
          class="absolute top-3 left-3 w-10 h-10 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-cyan-300/40"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="absolute top-3 right-3 w-10 h-10 border-t-2 border-r-2 border-cyan-300/40"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="absolute bottom-3 left-3 w-10 h-10 border-b-2 border-l-2 border-cyan-300/40"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="absolute bottom-3 right-3 w-10 h-10 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-cyan-300/40"
        >
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10">
          <!-- MENSAJE PRINCIPAL -->
          <div id="mensaje-despedida">
            <p
              class="font-charm text-2xl md:text-xl lg:text-2xl leading-relaxed mb-6 texto-mensaje"
            >
              Con la bendición de Dios y el amor de toda mi familia,
              <span class="texto-destacsado">me siento muy feliz</span>
              de llegar a este momento tan especial de mi vida. Ahora empieza un camino
              lleno de
              <span class="texto-destacasdo">sueños e ilusiones</span>
              que, con mucha fe, humildad y esperanza, deseo cumplir. Quisiera, con
              inmensa alegría,
              <span class="texto-destacadso">compartir este comienzo</span>
              de esta bella etapa junto a todos ustedes.
            </p>

            <!-- Línea decorativa -->
            <div
              class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 my-4"
              id="linea-decorativa"
            >
              <div class="w-16 h-[1px] linea-grad-izq"></div>
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 icono-corazon"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
              <div class="w-16 h-[1px] linea-grad-der"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- SECCIÓN CONFIRMAR ASISTENCIA -->
          <div id="seccion-confirmar" class="mt-2">
            <p
              class="font-charm text-2xl md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-2 texto-mensaje"
              id="texto-confirmar"
            >
              Tu presencia es muy importante para mí. Por favor,
              <span class="texto-destacadso">confirma tu asistencia</span>
              para compartir juntos este día tan especial.
            </p>

            <p
              class="font-charm pt-10 text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-8 texto-confirmar-titulo"
              id="mensaje-confirmar"
            >
              Por favor, haz clic para confirmar asistencia
            </p>

            <!-- BOTÓN CONFIRMAR ASISTENCIA GENERADO -->
            <div class="flex justify-center" id="boton-confirmar">
              <a
                href="https://wa.link/ab6zzp"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                aria-label="Confirmar asistencia por WhatsApp"
                class="boton-confirmar-custom group"
                style="white-space:nowrap;"
              >
                <!-- Icono WhatsApp -->
                <svg
                  class="boton-icon"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="currentColor"
                >
                  <path
                    d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
                <span
                  class="font-charm text-lg font-bold boton-texto"
                  style="white-space:nowrap;">Confirmar Asistencia</span
                >
                <span class="boton-brillo"></span>
              </a>
            </div>

            <!-- MENSAJE FINAL -->
            <p
              class="font-charm pt-10 text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-8 mensaje-final-texto"
              id="mensaje-final"
            >
              ¡Los espero con mucho cariño!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  import { gsap } from "gsap";
  import { ScrollTrigger } from "gsap/ScrollTrigger";

  gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);

  if (typeof window !== "undefined") {
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
      gsap.set("#flores-arriba-despedida", { opacity: 0, y: -30, scale: 0.8 });
      gsap.set("#card-despedida", { opacity: 0, y: 40, scale: 0.95 });
      gsap.set("#mensaje-despedida", {
        opacity: 0,
        y: 30,
        filter: "blur(5px)",
      });
      gsap.set("#linea-decorativa", { opacity: 0, scale: 0.5 });
      gsap.set("#texto-confirmar", { opacity: 0, y: 20 });
      gsap.set("#mensaje-confirmar", { opacity: 0, scale: 0.9, y: 20 });
      gsap.set("#boton-confirmar", { opacity: 0, scale: 0.8, y: 20 });
      gsap.set("#mensaje-final", { opacity: 0, scale: 0.9, y: 20 });

      ScrollTrigger.create({
        trigger: "#flores-arriba-despedida",
        start: "top 85%",
        onEnter: () => {
          const tl = gsap.timeline();

          tl.to("#flores-arriba-despedida", {
            opacity: 0.9,
            y: 0,
            scale: 1,
            duration: 0.8,
            ease: "back.out(1.5)",
          })
            .to(
              "#card-despedida",
              { opacity: 1, y: 0, scale: 1, duration: 0.8, ease: "power3.out" },
              0,
            )
            .to(
              "#mensaje-despedida",
              {
                opacity: 1,
                y: 0,
                filter: "blur(0px)",
                duration: 0.8,
                ease: "power2.out",
              },
              0,
            )
            .to(
              "#linea-decorativa",
              { opacity: 1, scale: 1, duration: 0.8, ease: "back.out(1.5)" },
              0,
            )
            .to(
              "#texto-confirmar",
              { opacity: 1, y: 0, duration: 0.8, ease: "power2.out" },
              0,
            )
            .to(
              "#mensaje-confirmar",
              {
                opacity: 1,
                scale: 1,
                y: 0,
                duration: 0.8,
                ease: "back.out(1.5)",
              },
              0,
            )
            .to(
              "#boton-confirmar",
              {
                opacity: 1,
                scale: 1,
                y: 0,
                duration: 0.8,
                ease: "back.out(1.5)",
              },
              0,
            )
            .to(
              "#mensaje-final",
              {
                opacity: 1,
                scale: 1,
                y: 0,
                duration: 0.8,
                ease: "elastic.out(1, 0.5)",
              },
              0,
            );

          // Animaciones continuas
          gsap.to("#linea-decorativa svg", {
            scale: 1.2,
            duration: 1.5,
            ease: "sine.inOut",
            yoyo: true,
            repeat: -1,
            delay: 0.8,
          });

          gsap.to("#mensaje-final", {
            textShadow:
              "0 0 20px rgba(0,232,255,0.8), 0 0 40px rgba(0,232,255,0.4)",
            duration: 2,
            ease: "sine.inOut",
            yoyo: true,
            repeat: -1,
            delay: 0.8,
          });

          gsap.to(".boton-confirmar-custom", {
            boxShadow:
              "0 0 28px rgba(0,232,255,0.7), 0 0 50px rgba(0,232,255,0.3)",
            duration: 2,
            ease: "sine.inOut",
            yoyo: true,
            repeat: -1,
            delay: 1.5,
          });

          // Destellos
          gsap.to(".sparkle-1", {
            y: -6,
            opacity: 0.6,
            duration: 2.8,
            ease: "sine.inOut",
            yoyo: true,
            repeat: -1,
          });
          gsap.to(".sparkle-2", {
            y: -4,
            opacity: 0.4,
            duration: 3.4,
            ease: "sine.inOut",
            yoyo: true,
            repeat: -1,
            delay: 0.8,
          });
          gsap.to(".sparkle-3", {
            y: -8,
            opacity: 0.5,
            duration: 2.2,
            ease: "sine.inOut",
            yoyo: true,
            repeat: -1,
            delay: 1.5,
          });
        },
        onLeaveBack: () => {
          gsap.set("#flores-arriba-despedida", {
            opacity: 0,
            y: -30,
            scale: 0.8,
          });
          gsap.set("#card-despedida", { opacity: 0, y: 40, scale: 0.95 });
          gsap.set("#mensaje-despedida", {
            opacity: 0,
            y: 30,
            filter: "blur(5px)",
          });
          gsap.set("#linea-decorativa", { opacity: 0, scale: 0.5 });
          gsap.set("#texto-confirmar", { opacity: 0, y: 20 });
          gsap.set("#mensaje-confirmar", { opacity: 0, scale: 0.9, y: 20 });
          gsap.set("#boton-confirmar", { opacity: 0, scale: 0.8, y: 20 });
          gsap.set("#mensaje-final", { opacity: 0, scale: 0.9, y: 20 });
        },
      });
    });
  }
</script>

<style>
  /* ─── CARD GLASSMORPHISM ─── */
  .cal-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
    box-shadow:
      0 8px 40px rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.18),
      0 2px 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  .cal-card::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -1px;
    left: 10%;
    width: 80%;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      transparent,
      rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.7),
      #fff,
      rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.7),
      transparent
    );
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .cal-card::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(
      ellipse at 50% 0%,
      rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.08) 0%,
      transparent 70%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* ─── TEXTOS ─── */
  .texto-mensaje {
    color: #ffffff;
    text-shadow:
      0 1px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5),
      0 0 12px rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.15);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .texto-destacado {
    color: #00e8ff;
    text-shadow:
      0 0 10px rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.7),
      0 0 20px rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.3);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .texto-confirmar-titulo {
    color: #ffffff;
    text-shadow:
      0 0 20px rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.8),
      0 0 40px rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.4),
      0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
  }

  .mensaje-final-texto {
    color: #00e8ff;
    text-shadow:
      0 0 16px rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.9),
      0 0 32px rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.5),
      0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  /* ─── LÍNEA DECORATIVA ─── */
  .linea-grad-izq {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.7));
  }

  .linea-grad-der {
    background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.7));
  }

  .icono-corazon {
    color: #00e8ff;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.8));
  }

  /* ─── BOTÓN CONFIRMAR ─── */
  .boton-confirmar-custom {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 14px 36px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.2) 0%,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12) 50%,
      rgba(0, 184, 204, 0.2) 100%
    );
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    box-shadow:
      0 0 16px rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.35),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    cursor: pointer;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition:
      transform 0.3s ease,
      border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .boton-confirmar-custom:hover {
    transform: scale(1.06) translateY(-2px);
    border-color: rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.95);
  }

  .boton-icon {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    color: #00e8ff;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.8));
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .boton-texto {
    color: #ffffff;
    text-shadow:
      0 0 10px rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.7),
      0 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .boton-brillo {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: -75%;
    width: 50%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      transparent,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25),
      transparent
    );
    transform: skewX(-20deg);
    transition: left 0.5s ease;
  }

  .boton-confirmar-custom:hover .boton-brillo {
    left: 125%;
  }

  /* ─── DESTELLOS ─── */
  .sparkle {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .sparkle-1 {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: #00e8ff;
    top: 8%;
    right: 6%;
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px 3px rgba(0, 232, 255, 0.6);
  }
  .sparkle-2 {
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    background: #fff;
    top: 15%;
    left: 8%;
    box-shadow: 0 0 6px 2px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }
  .sparkle-3 {
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    background: #7df4ff;
    bottom: 10%;
    right: 10%;
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px 3px rgba(125, 244, 255, 0.5);
  }
</style>
